longBusinessSummary: Arvida Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, owns, develops, and operates retirement villages and care facilities for the elderly in New Zealand. It operated various retirement villages with aged care beds and retirement units. The company was formerly known as Hercules Limited. Arvida Group Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Auckland, New Zealand.
